**Deliverables:**

| # | Deliverable | Artifact type |
|---|---|---|
| 1 | Collateral Risk Registry (`MCTI Schema v0.1`) | Machine-readable, versioned, signed |
| 2 | Structural Attribute Diff Stream | Event stream on covered assets |
