## (6) Deferring the quant model to "What Comes Next" — credibility hit?

**Net appropriate right-sizing; execution is slightly risky.**

- **Right call:** the debate explicitly recommended this. Quant calibration in thin-history regimes is the single most vulnerable claim. Moving it out is correct.
