## The Substrate-vs-Product Critique — Where the Moderator Is Right and Your Renaming Is Necessary but Insufficient

Your noun swaps are directionally right. But if the **budget line items and milestone gates still price the product**, cosmetic reframing won't survive governance scrutiny. It will look like rebranding without restructuring.

